獎<br />\n華佗生物或醫學獎<br />\n李白文學獎<br />\n孔子和平獎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劉徽數學獎<br />\n商高幾何學獎<br />\n朱載玉音樂獎"},{"pid":"706702d1e22c33ba597d2b2b97983639445f8af7","tid":422970,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>只係亞洲科研遲起步者，過多3,40年應該同鬼佬五五開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過黑鬼就算9數喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n力架其實有potential拎和平獎"},{"pid":"c0ad6a113d108c6e2e0c90a2f465b334b9a03657","tid":422970,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>張衡物理學獎<br />\n劉安化學獎<br />\n華佗生物或醫學獎<br />\n李白文學獎<br />\n孔子和平獎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劉徽數學獎<br />\n商高幾何學獎<br />\n朱載玉音樂獎</blockquote><br />\n神農氏醫學獎"},{"pid":"fb21ebdee1f60ab7c3ad3d0a6ab4de0d29ee94cf","tid":422970,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>只係亞洲科研遲起步者，過多3,40年應該同鬼佬五五開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n東亞咪得日本人可以勉強追下<br />\n<br />\n其他難d啦</blockquote><br />\n淨計科學，日本得主數量排世界第五</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果Nobel prize有假論文獎<br />\n仲唔係我地天朝上国攞哂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ae234b7ec9a850ac3f4755b6cae269e029085c","tid":422970,"uid":16707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃種人同黑鬼係廢呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n世界上有好多文學家作家都出色過文學獎得主，攞獎只係一個成就。<br />\n北島既詩對人性既探求好到位，高概括力既用字同一針見血既簡潔行文絕對夠攞文學獎有突。剩係佢寫既宣告同回答表現出對共產黨同中國式邏輯既批判已經可見一斑，但佢最盡只有文學獎提名。我覺得佢比莫言更值得攞文學獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f0c5b7bdd3cc1f6d00ae5578afb6ccb5d4dffc","tid":422970,"uid":19